Interface Filter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BloomFilter, CuckooFilter, ScalableBloomFilter, StableBloomFilter

    public interface Filter
extends java.io.Closeable
    Common filter interface. Note: method remove(String) and remove(Set) may be not implemented in particular implementations.
